testsuite.name: Scenario: Load EQE from CDN

testcase.name: Given I am logged in as the default administrator
When I navigate to the System Settings page
And I set Use CDN to true
And The Use CDN checkbox is true
And I submit the changes to System Settings
Then The changes to System Settings were successfully saved.
Then I navigate to the System Homepage
Then I am on the Content Repository page of Demonstration Class
When I choose creating new question/Text from the main dropdown button
And I click inside the question text editor
And I click Equation Editor button to open the Math Editor dialog and assert that the Math Editor dialog is visible
Then I click Done in the Math Editor dialog
